        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine State Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Uniform Time Act of 1966 to provide that the standard time for Florida shall permanently be Coordinated Universal Time retarded by four hours (Daylight Saving Time for the Eastern time zone). </p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
